{"questionId":"8899448","questionHtml":"<p>A bird of weight <em><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>W</mi></math></em> sits on a thin rope at its midpoint. The rope is almost horizontal and has negligible mass.</p>\n<p><img style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;\" src=\"__IMG__/26ef8850ab5a7a618dd6c4ea13623b1248af9c7c.png\"></p>\n<p>The tension in the rope is</p>\n<p><br>A.&nbsp;&nbsp;less than <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mi>W</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>B.&nbsp;&nbsp;equal to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mi>W</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>C.&nbsp;&nbsp;between <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mi>W</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>W</mi></math></p>\n<p>D.&nbsp;&nbsp;greater than&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>W</mi></math></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>D</p>","meta":{"questionId":"8899448","referenceCode":"SPM.1A.HL.TZ0.8","subjectId":"59-dp-physics-first-assessment-2025","title":"A bird of weight W sits on a thin rope at its midpoint. The rope is almost horizontal and has negligible mass. The tension in the rope is A. less than W2 B. equal to W2 C. between ","paper":"1A","level":"HL","questionNumber":"8","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["A. Space, time and motion","A. Space, time and motion","A.2 Forces and momentum"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}